ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c160%2c20220513%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,訴,160,20220513,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"160","JDATE":"20220513","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}